title: Matt Harvey on missing playoff workout due to traffic: 'I just screwed up'
text:
advertisement | advertise on newsday 
Harvey, the only player not to make the workout, is slated to pitch Game 3 of the NLDS against the Dodgers. 
"I'm concerned about the guys who are here," said Mets captain David Wright, who sidestepped a question about Harvey. "The guys who are here had a great workout."
